  abstract = {In this article, we propose a novel family of Lie algebra valued functions on the special orthogonal group SO(3). Each function belonging to this family induces a novel controller that stabilizes a rigid body attitude. All controllers induced by the family form a controller class. This novel controller class contains both local and almost-global asymptotically stable controllers, and this article presents geometric stability results of the whole controller class.},
